propel.core.collections.arrays
Class ReifiedArray<T>

java.lang.Object
  propel.core.collections.arrays.ReifiedArray<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>
public class ReifiedArray<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>

Encapsulates a primitive or object array. For primitive arrays, you must specify System.Object as generic type parameter, to allow for boxing.
